##_______________________________________________________________________________
## Plot the values of the geometrical delays

set title "Geometrical delays"
set xlabel "Antenna number"
set ylabel "Sky pixel number"
set zlabel "Geometrical delay [s]"
set contour base
set term pdf color solid enhanced
set output "skymap-delays.pdf"
splot "skymap-delays.dat" u 1:2:3 w l

